Titolo: Arc the Lad II

Anno: 1996

Descrizione: Arc the Lad II is a tactical role-playing video game developed by ARC Entertainment and published by Sony Computer Entertainment exclusively for the PlayStation.
The story continues from the first game, although the focus shifts from Arc to Elc. It expands from the gameplay of the first installment, with a larger world and a more diverse cast. An anime series was made based on this game.

Genere: Tactical role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
